@startuml
skinparam participantBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam lifelineStrategy solid

actor "Khách hàng" as User #Yellow
boundary "ContactPage" as UI #Yellow
boundary "AxiosClient" as API #Yellow
control "ContactController" as Ctrl #Yellow
control "ContactService" as Svc #Yellow
entity "ContactMessage" as CEnt #Yellow
database "PostgreSQL" as DB #Yellow

User -> UI : 1: Mở trang liên hệ /contact
activate UI
UI -> UI : 1.1: Hiển thị form:\n- Name (required)\n- Email (required)\n- Subject (dropdown 5 lựa chọn)\n- Message (textarea)

User -> UI : 2: Điền form và nhấn Submit
activate UI
UI -> UI : 2.1: Gán state: isSubmitting = true\nsubmitError = ''
UI -> API : 2.2: POST /api/Contact\nBody: CreateContactRequest\n{ name, email, subject, message }
activate API

note right of API : Public endpoint - không cần JWT

API -> Ctrl : 2.3: Chuyển tiếp request
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> Ctrl : 2.4: FluentValidation:\nCreateContactRequestValidator
alt 2.5: [Validation thất bại]
Ctrl --> API : 2.5.1: 400 Bad Request\n(validation errors)
API --> UI : 2.5.2: Response lỗi
UI -> UI : 2.5.3: setSubmitError(message)
UI --> User : 2.5.4: Hiển thị lỗi validation
else 2.6: [Validation thành công]
Ctrl -> Svc : 2.6.1: CreateAsync(request)
activate Svc

Svc -> Svc : 2.6.2: _mapper.Map<ContactMessage>(request)\n(Name, Email, Subject, Message)
Svc -> Svc : 2.6.3: contact.CreatedAt = UtcNow\ncontact.IsRead = false

Svc -> DB : 2.6.4: ContactMessages.AddAsync(contact)
activate DB
DB --> Svc : OK
deactivate DB
Svc -> DB : 2.6.5: SaveChangesAsync()
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 2.6.5.1: OK
deactivate DB

Svc -> Svc : 2.6.6: _mapper.Map<ContactResponse>(contact)
Svc --> Ctrl : 2.6.7: ApiResponse.Ok(data,\n"Message sent successfully")
deactivate Svc
Ctrl --> API : 2.7: 200 OK
deactivate Ctrl
API --> UI : 2.8: Response success
deactivate API

UI -> UI : 2.9: setSubmitSuccess(true)\nsetIsSubmitting(false)\nReset form về giá trị mặc định
UI -> UI : 2.10: setTimeout 3s -> setSubmitSuccess(false)
UI --> User : 2.11: Hiển thị "Message Sent!"\nkèm icon check_circle
deactivate UI

end

@enduml
